1.
 Purpose
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy establishes mandatory rules of behavior governing the acceptable use of Elko County Information Technology (IT) resources.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection*

\lang english
2.
 Scope
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy applies to all users granted access to County IT resources,
 including employees,
 elected officials,
 contractors,
 vendors,
 interns,
 and volunteers.
 County IT resources include County-owned,
 County-managed,
 and County-provisioned systems and services,
 including endpoints,
 networks,
 applications,
 cloud services,
 accounts,
 and County data.
\end_layout

